extends layout

block content

    //-Origin Story 
    section(class='about-us') 
        h1(class='about-title') Our Story

        img(class='donut-shop' src='/images/Starbucks.png' alt='Credit goes to Starbucks ')
        p Downtown Donuts has been serving the heart of downtown since 1992. What started as a small family kitchen with a few simple recipes has grown into a beloved community staple. Every donut we make is crafted by hand using the same recipes passed down through our family for over three decades.
        p Our mission is simple — bring people together over great food. We believe that a good donut and a warm cup of coffee can turn any morning around. We are committed to using quality ingredients, supporting local suppliers, and treating every customer like family.
        p Founded by John and Mary Doe in 1992, Downtown Donuts has always been a family operation. Today their children and grandchildren continue the tradition, showing up every morning before dawn to make sure the donuts are fresh and the coffee is hot when you walk through the door.


        






